<h2 id="overview-of-project-steps">E. Overview of Project Steps</h2>
<p>
  The retro-commissioning project was conducted using the following steps:
</p>
<ol>
  <li>Planning Phase: Develop project goals, scope, and schedule</li>
  <li>Investigation Phase: Conduct site assessment, review documentation, and perform diagnostic testing</li>
  <li>Implementation Phase: Implement selected measures and verify results</li>
  <li>Hand-off Phase: Provide training and documentation to facility staff</li>
</ol>

